to expect something","p":"ænˈtɪsɪpeɪt","ex":"We don't anticipate any major problems.","e":"anticipate","pos":2,"m":"thấy trước, chặn trước, lường trước"},{"om":"the state of feeling nervous or worried that something bad is going to happen","p":"æŋˈzaɪəti","ex":"acute/intense/deep anxiety","e":"anxiety","pos":1,"m":"mối lo âu, sự lo lắng"},{"om":"feeling worried or nervous","p":"ˈæŋkʃəs","ex":"He seemed anxious about the meeting.","e":"anxious","pos":3,"m":"lo âu, lo lắng, băn khoăn"},{"p":"'æɳkʃəsli","e":"anxiously","pos":4,"m":"lo âu, lo lắng, băn khoăn"},{"om":"any person at all; it does not matter who","p":"ˈeniwʌn","ex":"Is anyone there?","e":"anyone","m":"người nào, bất cứ ai"},{"om":"any thing at all, when it does not matter which","p":"ˈeniθɪŋ","ex":"Would you like anything else?","e":"anything","pos":5,"m":"việc gì, vật gì; bất cứ việc gì, vật gì"},{"om":"despite something; even so","p":"ˈeniweɪ","ex":"It's too expensive and anyway the colour doesn't suit you.","e":"anyway","pos":4,"m":"thế nào cũng được, dù sao chăng nữa"},{"om":"in, at or to any place, when it does not matter where","p":"ˈeniwer","ex":"I can't see it anywhere.","e":"anywhere","pos":4,"m":"bất cứ chỗ nào, bất cứ nơi đâu"},{"om":"separated by a distance, of space or time","p":"əˈpɑːrt","ex":"The two houses stood 500 metres apart.","e":"apart","pos":4,"m":"về một bên, qua một bên"},{"om":"a set of rooms for living in, usually on one floor of a building","p":"əˈpɑːrtmənt","ex":"self-catering holiday apartments","e":"apartment","pos":1,"m":"căn phòng, căn buồng"},{"om":"to say that you are sorry for doing something wrong or causing a problem","p":"əˈpɑːlədʒaɪz","ex":"Why should I apologize?","e":"apologize","m":"xin lỗi, tạ lỗi"},{"om":"easy to see or understand","p":"əˈpærənt","ex":"Their devotion was apparent.","e":"apparent","pos":3,"m":"rõ ràng, rành mạch; bề ngoài, có vẻ"},{"om":"to make a formal request to a court or to somebody in authority for a judgement or a decision to be changed","p