ument","pos":1,"m":"lý lẽ"},{"om":"to happen; to start to exist","p":"əˈraɪz","ex":"A new crisis has arisen.","e":"arise","pos":2,"m":"xuất hiện, nảy ra, nảy sinh ra"},{"om":"to provide weapons for yourself/somebody in order to fight a battle or a war","p":"ɑːrm","ex":"The country was arming against the enemy.","e":"arm","m":"cánh tay; vũ trang, trang bị (vũ khí)"},{"om":"involving the use of weapons","p":"ɑːrmd","ex":"an armed robbery","e":"armed","pos":3,"m":"vũ trang"},{"om":"a large organized group of soldiers who are trained to fight on land","p":"ˈɑːrmi","ex":"The two opposing armies faced each other across the battlefield.","e":"army","pos":1,"m":"quân đội"},{"om":"surrounding somebody/something; on each side of something","p":"əˈraʊnd","ex":"The house is built around a central courtyard.","e":"around","m":"xung quanh, vòng quanh"},{"om":"to plan or organize something in advance","p":"əˈreɪndʒ","ex":"The party was arranged quickly.","e":"arrange","pos":2,"m":"sắp xếp, sắp đặt, sửa soạn"},{"om":"a plan or preparation that you make so that something can happen","p":"əˈreɪndʒmənt","ex":"travel arrangements","e":"arrangement","pos":1,"m":"sự sắp xếp, sắp đặt, sự sửa soạn"},{"om":"the act of arresting somebody","p":"əˈrest","ex":"The police made several arrests.","e":"arrest","m":"bắt giữ, sự bắt giữ"},{"om":"an act of coming or being brought to a place","p":"əˈraɪvl","ex":"Guests receive dinner on/upon arrival at the hotel.","e":"arrival","pos":1,"m":"sự đến, sự tới nơi"},{"om":"to get to a place, especially at the end of a journey","p":"əˈraɪv","ex":"I'll wait until they arrive.","e":"arrive","pos":2,"m":"đến, tới nơi"},{"om":"a thin stick with a sharp point at one end, which is shot from a bow","p":"ˈæroʊ","ex":"a bow and arrow","e":"arrow","pos":1,"m":"tên, mũi tên"},{"om":"the use of the imagination to express ideas or feelings, particularly in painting, drawing or sculpture","p":"ɑːrt","ex":"modern/contemporary/American art","e":"art","pos":1,"m":"nghệ thuật